dc_description_s: France. Bureau de recherches geologiques et minieres [BRGM]. Carte geologique CG-121(1954) France. Service de la carte geologique de France North Decimal Degree 47.3387 South Decimal Degree 46.9789 East Decimal Degree 1.9137 West Decimal Degree 1.0667 Relief shown by hachures. Longitude is given in centesimal values (100 grades = 90 degrees) .The Service de la carte geologique de la France was integrated to the BRGM to become the only France Service geologique national. Based on "Carte topograqphique de l'etat major."
